   </video>
  </div>
 </p>
 <p class="bb_paragraph">
 </p>
 <p class="bb_paragraph">
  <strong>
   Key Features:
  </strong>
 </p>
 <ul class="bb_ul">
  <li>
   <p class="bb_paragraph">
    3D figure production and customization
   </p>
  </li>
  <li>
   <p class="bb_paragraph">
    Shelf management, pricing, and customer satisfaction
   </p>
  </li>
  <li>
   <p class="bb_paragraph">
    Expand your store and personalize its design
   </p>
  </li>
  <li>
   <p class="bb_paragraph">
    Create collection sets and discover rare figures
   </p>
  </li>
  <li>
   <p class="bb_paragraph">
    Follow market trends and identify best-selling products
   </p>
  </li>
 </ul>
 <p class="bb_paragraph">
  Build your shop from the ground up and become the biggest name in the figure collecting world!
 </p>
 <p class="bb_paragraph">
 </p>
 <p class="bb_paragraph">
  <div class="bb_img_ctn">
